  "imageCount": 11,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b9c6089cda2039a5.jpg?v=1782535364\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So delighted to be a part of the <a href=\"http://ohlovelovely.blogspot.com/p/pendant-project.html\">Pendant Project</a>. AesaLina asked if I wanted to be one of the muses for it, and how could I say no? \"The <strong>goal </strong>of my PendantProject is to provide inspiration and encourage others to create and indulge in their own handmade accessories.\" Thanks <a href=\"http://ohlovelovely.blogspot.com/\">AesaLina</a> for including me in this group of creatives. You can see what <a href=\"http://papernstitchblog.com/2012/02/09/diy-idea-stitching-together-a-pendant-necklace-giveaway/\">papernstitch</a> and <a href=\"http://hartandsew.blogspot.com/2012/02/pendant-project-giveaway.html\">hart + sew</a> did with theirs. Next week, Caitlin of <a href=\"http://www.hueandhum.com/\">hue &amp; hum</a> will be revealing hers. Love how unique and lovely everyone's creations are using the same blank \"<a href=\"http://lovelovely.storenvy.com/products/222422-stitchery-wooden-pendant\">canvas</a>\". </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e711424b75735155.jpg?v=1782535367\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>I knew I would be taking a chance by stamping on my pendant and not having it turn out how I envisioned. Decided to simply try stamping it since I could always flip it over to the back if I messed it up. I used the <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=lovestruck&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D36752%2F59151%2DLOVESTRUCK%2DLOVE%2DSTRUCK%2FDetail\">camera from the LoveStruck stamp set</a> and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=versafine&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D23812%2FVersaFine%2DONYX%2DBLACK%2DInk%2FDetail\">Versafine ink</a>. I told myself \"be fearless\", even with your little craft projects.  </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/66bcfe41a09ba8a4.jpg?v=1782535370\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>And thankfully, it worked. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6393044f2d060503.jpg?v=1782535372\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Then I began stitching. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"16e-dsc_0328.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2d148bc40b04fbcb.jpg?v=1782535375\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16f-dsc_0330.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7f8b8d83f0536546.jpg?v=1782535378\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16h-dsc_0334.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e07935f336615083.jpg?v=1782535381\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16i-dsc_0336.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7bedfe6decb84047.jpg?v=1782535383\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16j-dsc_0337.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7c47d6cd521f18a0.jpg?v=1782535386\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16k-dsc_0338.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/69b3dc5864bb7a91.jpg?v=1782535389\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>After adding a jump ring and a chain, I put it on and snapped a photo with my iPhone.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6c99bd4130e0fc2a.jpg?v=1782535392\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>I may just have to stock up on some more of <a href=\"http://lovelovely.storenvy.com/products/222422-stitchery-wooden-pendant\">these pendants</a> for gifts. Thanks again <a href=\"http://lovelovely.storenvy.com/\">AesaLina!</a></p><p><strong>*****Now for the really fun part. You all get a chance to win your own pendant. Simply leave a comment telling me something lovely.</strong> Winner will be announced on Monday, February 27. Good luck! </p>"
}